block_list.title: Video Tutorial
block_list.body: This Origami Rosette by Paul Jackson is a really wonderful model. It is the perfect decoration arond the house. This origami rosette is 100% pure origami, no glue and no tape. The design of this model uses a fan lock. When you open it up, it just snaps into this wonderful rosette shape. I hope you enjoy it!!! Thanks for watching! Wilson Lee@Heap Art
